The Sensor has 4 pins

(1) Power
(2) Ground
(3) Trigger
(4) Echo

 STEPS
(1) connect the 4 pins as seen in the circuit diagram
(2) Download attached Arduino code or write new code following the code given
(3) Connect Arduino Board to Computer and select the board on the top of the arduino IDE
(4) Upload code 
(5) click on serial monitor to view output
